products.name: Sourdough Grains & Seeds
products.description: Abbott's Bakery Sourdough Grains & Seeds Sandwich Slice Bread Loaf
products.details: Turn your everyday meal into a gourmet delight with Abbott’s Bakery® Sourdough. This loaf is bursting with flavour and texture from our special blend of 11 grains and seeds which perfectly complements the mild sourdough taste. A sprinkle of coarsely ground pumpkin seeds adds an irresistible crunch sensation while tantalising your tastebuds.
products.ingredients: Wheat Flour, Water, Baker's Yeast, Seeds (5%) (Sunflower Seeds, Poppy Seed, Linseed, Pumpkin Seeds (0.7%)), Mixed Grains (3.5%) (Kibbled Rye, Kibbled Wheat, Kibbled Triticale, Buckwheat, Kibbled Corn, Rolled Oats, Kibbled Barley), Dried Wheat Sourdough (3%), Wheat Gluten, Canola Oil, Vinegar, Kibbled Soy, Iodised Salt, Soy Flour, Emulsifiers (471, 472e, 481), Vitamins (Thiamin, Folic Acid).

products.name: Harvest seeds & grains
products.description: Abbott's Village Bakery - Bread Harvest - Seeds & Grains
products.details: Now here’s an interesting loaf. A blend of canola seeds, linseeds, sunflower seeds and sesame seeds give extra pop when eaten fresh. And if you listen closely when you toast it, you’ll even hear those seeds pop. But why stop there? A sesame seed topping adds a roasted nutty flavour.

The perfect no fuss option for breakfast or dessert.
